premise_source_doc_sentence: Michael Schumacher received praise from many within the Formula One community , including former Champion Jody Scheckter and Ferrari president Luca di Montezemolo , though he was criticised by former Italian president Francesco Cossiga for his conduct when the Italian National Anthem was played on the podium .
